WEBVTT

00:00:02.503 --> 00:00:04.204
NARRATOR During
Ash's first Gym badge

00:00:04.204 --> 00:00:06.006
challenge in the
Kalos region

00:00:06.006 --> 00:00:08.408
our heroes battled Viola,
the Santalune Gym Leader.

00:00:10.477 --> 00:00:12.679
But because Pikachu
and Fletchling found it

00:00:12.679 --> 00:00:15.249
impossible to move freely
on the battlefield

