Looks like
another machine went boom.

00:06:55.916 --> 00:06:59.719
[grunts]
Why? Why?

00:06:59.719 --> 00:07:01.755
Okay, in that case..

00:07:01.755 --> 00:07:03.590
Alright, Froakie, I choose you!

00:07:06.960 --> 00:07:08.828
[PLEASED]

00:07:08.828 --> 00:07:10.997
If you attack us
with your Frubbles

00:07:10.997 --> 00:07:12.565
it'll be like getting
attacked with Sticky Web.

00:07:12.565 --> 00:07:13.967
[CONFIDENT]

00:07:13.967 --> 00:07:15.869
[FRUBBLES MOVE]

00:07:15.869 --> 00:07:17.003
Quick, Pikachu, Fletchling,
dodge it!

00:07:17.003 --> 00:07:19.539
[EXERTION]

00:07:21.508 --> 00:07:23.843
Wow! What a clever way
to use Frubbles.

00:07:23.843 --> 00:07:25.011
Yeah, keep it up!

00:07:25.011 --> 00:07:26.379
[EXCITED]

00:07:26.379 --> 00:07:28.648
Now, concentrate and speed up!

00:07:28.648 --> 00:07:31.117
[CONFIDENT]
[FRUBBLES MOVE]

