That Froakie's
from Professor Sycamore's

00:07:37.724 --> 00:07:39.759
research lab.

00:07:39.759 --> 00:07:40.860
SERENA
Just like my Fennekin.

00:07:40.860 --> 00:07:43.530
[EXERTION]

00:07:45.865 --> 00:07:47.934
[SATISFIED]

00:07:47.934 --> 00:07:50.370
I think
we're gonna be just fine.

