[PROUD]

00:07:59.813 --> 00:08:02.615
♪ Ra ra ra go team go ♪♪

00:08:02.615 --> 00:08:04.617
I know you can do it.
You're awesome.

00:08:04.617 --> 00:08:06.586
Bonnie, I think it's bedtime.

00:08:06.586 --> 00:08:09.522
Mm, you were great.

00:08:09.522 --> 00:08:12.492
‐ Yeah, weren't they? Let's go.
