00:12:03.957 --> 00:12:06.192
[CONFIDENT]/[FRUSTRATED]

00:12:07.827 --> 00:12:11.231
It's just like the last battle.

00:12:11.231 --> 00:12:13.466
The difference is Ash trained
really hard for this one.

00:12:13.466 --> 00:12:17.337
Can you get up, Pikachu?
[EFFORT]

00:12:17.337 --> 00:12:19.906
This ice battlefield
is my studio!

00:12:19.906 --> 00:12:22.008
I'm the photographer
and I call the shots.

00:12:22.008 --> 00:12:24.944
Surskit, Signal Beam!

00:12:24.944 --> 00:12:26.179
Now, Pikachu!

00:12:26.179 --> 00:12:27.614
[EXERTION]

00:12:27.614 --> 00:12:29.282
‐ Aah!
‐ Wow!

00:12:29.282 --> 00:12:31.918
That's the thing
Ash wouldn't tell us about.

00:12:31.918 --> 00:12:33.953
'How he was going to deal
with the ice battlefield.'

00:12:33.953 --> 00:12:35.822
Way to go!
Now, use Thunderbolt!

00:12:35.822 --> 00:12:37.590
[THUNDERBOLT MOVE]
[SIGNAL BEAM MOVE]

00:12:42.095 --> 00:12:43.863
[PAINED]

00:12:45.231 --> 00:12:46.466
Surskit, no!

00:12:46.466 --> 00:12:50.003
[STUNNED]

00:12:50.003 --> 00:12:51.938
Surskit is unable to battle.
Pikachu wins!

00:12:51.938 --> 00:12:53.339
[FATIGUED]

00:12:53.339 --> 00:12:54.907
We did it!

00:12:54.907 --> 00:12:56.342
[TRIUMPHANT]

00:12:56.342 --> 00:12:57.277
‐ Yay!
‐ Yay!

00:12:57.277 --> 00:12:59.279
[ECSTATIC]

00:12:59.279 --> 00:13:03.283
Who knew Pikachu would plant
its tail to stay balanced.

00:13:03.283 --> 00:13:05.685
Surskit, that was excellent.
Now get a good rest.

00:13:05.685 --> 00:13:07.887
Pikachu, return!

00:13:07.887 --> 00:13:10.290
[RELIEVED]

00:13:10.290 --> 00:13:13.226
What? You're done battling
with Pikachu?

00:13:13.226 --> 00:13:14.927
Fletchling wants
a chance for a rematch

00:13:14.927 --> 00:13:17.130
against Vivillon too.

00:13:17.130 --> 00:13:18.698
Fletchling, I choose you.

00:13:20.400 --> 00:13:22.035
[GRATEFUL]

00:13:22.035 --> 00:13:25.338
Picture‐perfect.
Let's do this, Vivillon!

00:13:25.338 --> 00:13:27.840
[EXERTION]

00:13:27.840 --> 00:13:30.743
They won't have to worry
about Sticky Web this time.

00:13:30.743 --> 00:13:33.079
And Ash can thank
Pikachu for that.

00:13:33.079 --> 00:13:35.081
They also have
a great counter for Gust!

00:13:35.081 --> 00:13:37.350
This's not yesterday's battle,
for sure.

00:13:37.350 --> 00:13:39.218
Alright, Fletchling,
Steel Wing, let's go!

00:13:39.218 --> 00:13:41.554
[INTENT]

00:13:41.554 --> 00:13:42.922
[EXERTION]

00:13:42.922 --> 00:13:44.457
[STEEL WING MOVE]

00:13:46.092 --> 00:13:47.427
Use Psychic!

00:13:47.427 --> 00:13:48.594
[PSYCHIC MOVE]

00:13:48.594 --> 00:13:51.030
[PAINED]/[ALARMED]

00:13:52.932 --> 00:13:55.768
[CONFIDENT]/[STRUGGLING]

00:13:55.768 --> 00:13:57.804
Fletchling! No!

00:13:57.804 --> 00:13:59.906
Be strong! Now, get up!

00:13:59.906 --> 00:14:01.407
[DETERMINED]

00:14:01.407 --> 00:14:03.743
Great, Fletchling! Steel Wing!

00:14:03.743 --> 00:14:06.179
[INTENT]/[STEEL WING MOVE]

00:14:06.179 --> 00:14:08.381
[PAINED]

00:14:08.381 --> 00:14:11.017
‐ Aah!
‐ Way to go! Now, use Peck!

00:14:11.017 --> 00:14:13.086
[PECK MOVE]

00:14:13.086 --> 00:14:14.821
Dodge it, quick!

00:14:14.821 --> 00:14:17.090
[EXERTION]/[DISAPPOINTED]

00:14:17.090 --> 00:14:18.524
Alright! Use Gust!

00:14:18.524 --> 00:14:21.160
[GUST MOVE]

00:14:23.062 --> 00:14:24.731
[PAINED]

00:14:24.731 --> 00:14:26.466
Remember our training,
Fletchling!

00:14:26.466 --> 00:14:27.700
[EMPATHETIC]

00:14:27.700 --> 00:14:30.169
[EFFORT]/[CONFIDENT]

00:14:32.338 --> 00:14:34.173
Great, Fletchling, ride it!

00:14:34.173 --> 00:14:35.842
‐ Yeah, you can do it!
‐ Yay!

00:14:35.842 --> 00:14:38.211
Fletchling,
use Razor Wind, now!

00:14:38.211 --> 00:14:41.447
[RAZOR WIND MOVE]
Vivillon, Sleep Powder!

00:14:41.447 --> 00:14:42.949
[SLEEP POWDER MOVE]

00:14:44.250 --> 00:14:45.518
[PAINED]

00:14:48.121 --> 00:14:50.323
‐ Fletchling, wake up!
‐ Ah!

00:14:50.323 --> 00:14:52.458
I had no idea Vivillon
could use Sleep Powder.

00:14:52.458 --> 00:14:53.659
Uh‐oh!

00:14:53.659 --> 00:14:56.295
[WORRIED]

00:14:56.295 --> 00:14:59.198
Excellent! Picture‐ perfect!
Vivillon, Solar Beam!

00:14:59.198 --> 00:15:00.800
[SOLAR BEAM MOVE]

00:15:03.236 --> 00:15:04.704
[PAINED]

00:15:04.704 --> 00:15:06.606
Oh, no! Fletchling!

00:15:08.441 --> 00:15:10.543
[CONCERNED]/[STUNNED]

00:15:10.543 --> 00:15:11.711
WOMAN #1 'Fletchling
is unable to battle!'

00:15:11.711 --> 00:15:13.646
'Vivillon wins!'

00:15:13.646 --> 00:15:15.581
Aw. Poor Fletchling lost.

00:15:15.581 --> 00:15:17.283
[SAD]

00:15:17.283 --> 00:15:19.085
There's no way my sister
would let Ash win

00:15:19.085 --> 00:15:20.586
without a real fight.

00:15:20.586 --> 00:15:22.188
‐ That's okay!
‐ Huh?

00:15:22.188 --> 00:15:23.623
‐ We believe in Ash.
‐ Hm.

00:15:26.058 --> 00:15:27.927
Good job,
you battled hard, Fletchling

00:15:27.927 --> 00:15:29.962
so get lots of rest.

00:15:29.962 --> 00:15:32.064
I'm gonna need you to get back
in there, Pikachu.

00:15:32.064 --> 00:15:34.467
[AFFIRMATIVE]/[CHALLENGING]

00:15:34.467 --> 00:15:37.170
Now, Vivillon, use Gust!

00:15:37.170 --> 00:15:40.606
[GUST MOVE]/[EFFORT]

00:15:40.606 --> 00:15:42.942
Hang tough, Pikachu!
You can stay on your feet.

00:15:42.942 --> 00:15:44.577
[STRUGGLING]

00:15:46.612 --> 00:15:47.847
Pikachu's still
feeling the effects

00:15:47.847 --> 00:15:49.749
of the battle with Surskit.

00:15:49.749 --> 00:15:52.185
If this drags on, it could be
at a real disadvantage.

00:15:52.185 --> 00:15:54.420
[DETERMINED]

00:15:54.420 --> 00:15:56.989
Pikachu can't beat
my Vivillon in that state.

00:15:56.989 --> 00:15:59.325
I'm afraid you're gonna have
to wait longer for your badge.

00:15:59.325 --> 00:16:01.127
Yeah, well,
there's no way we're giving up!

00:16:01.127 --> 00:16:02.962
That's not what we're about!

00:16:02.962 --> 00:16:04.297
We'll keep battling
right up until the very end!

00:16:06.199 --> 00:16:07.700
Don't give up till it's over.

00:16:09.435 --> 00:16:11.671
I admire your persistence.

00:16:11.671 --> 00:16:14.173
But this is the end.
Gust, one more time!

00:16:14.173 --> 00:16:17.410
[GUST MOVE]/[EFFORT]

00:16:17.410 --> 00:16:19.479
Pikachu! Iron Tail, let's go!

00:16:19.479 --> 00:16:22.114
[IRON TAIL MOVE]

00:16:24.851 --> 00:16:26.819
‐ Ah!
‐ It's using Iron Tail!

00:16:26.819 --> 00:16:29.121
Another great way to stay put.

00:16:29.121 --> 00:16:32.758
‐ Pikachu is so cool!
‐ 'Pretty clever.'

00:16:32.758 --> 00:16:35.261
But you just made it
even easier for me to focus.

00:16:35.261 --> 00:16:36.963
Vivillon, use Solar Beam!

00:16:36.963 --> 00:16:38.865
[SOLAR BEAM MOVE]

00:16:40.700 --> 00:16:42.435
Pikachu, use Thunderbolt!

00:16:42.435 --> 00:16:44.971
[THUNDERBOLT MOVE]

00:16:48.241 --> 00:16:50.610
[grunting]

00:16:50.610 --> 00:16:53.379
Vivillon, Sleep Powder!
[SLEEP POWDER MOVE]

00:16:53.379 --> 00:16:56.415
[ALARMED]
[PAINED]/[DAZED]

00:16:58.484 --> 00:17:00.319
‐ Pikachu!
‐ Oh!

00:17:00.319 --> 00:17:02.455
So, here we are.

00:17:02.455 --> 00:17:04.690
It's my chance to take
a great last picture.

00:17:04.690 --> 00:17:07.860
Pikachu! Ash!
You've got to hang in there.

00:17:07.860 --> 00:17:10.329
Let's finish this up,
Solar Beam!

00:17:10.329 --> 00:17:12.965
[SOLAR BEAM MOVE]
Pikachu! Wake up!

00:17:12.965 --> 00:17:15.434
[EFFORT]

00:17:15.434 --> 00:17:17.803
Remember your training
from yesterday!

00:17:17.803 --> 00:17:20.373
Ah! Pikachu!

00:17:20.373 --> 00:17:23.442
'Use Electro Ball on yourself!'
EXERTION]

00:17:23.442 --> 00:17:25.778
[ELECTRO BALL MOVE]

00:17:25.778 --> 00:17:26.979
[SURPRISED]

00:17:26.979 --> 00:17:28.414
[ELECTRO BALL MOVE]

00:17:35.154 --> 00:17:36.355
Aah!

00:17:36.355 --> 00:17:37.990
[DETERMINED]

00:17:40.059 --> 00:17:41.627
‐ Alright!
‐ Alright!

00:17:41.627 --> 00:17:44.697
It neutralized Sleep Powder with
an Electric‐type move on itself.

00:17:44.697 --> 00:17:46.566
[chuckles]
That's so very, very Ash.

00:17:46.566 --> 00:17:48.134
Vivillon, Solar Beam!

00:17:48.134 --> 00:17:50.603
[SOLAR BEAM MOVE]

00:17:50.603 --> 00:17:52.605
We're all with you, so put
everything into this move!

00:17:52.605 --> 00:17:53.940
Use Electro Ball!

00:17:53.940 --> 00:17:56.442
[ELECTRO BALL MOVE]

00:17:59.812 --> 00:18:01.714
[SURPRISED]
Vivillon, no!

00:18:01.714 --> 00:18:04.250
[WORRIED]/[PAINED]

00:18:09.155 --> 00:18:11.691
‐ Come on, Vivillon, be strong!
‐ Uh‐oh!

00:18:11.691 --> 00:18:14.060
Vivillon's flying kind
of weird all of a sudden.

00:18:14.060 --> 00:18:17.597
Look at its wing,
it's covered with ice.

00:18:17.597 --> 00:18:21.467
‐ No. How can this be?
‐ Pikachu! Now, use Thunderbolt!

00:18:21.467 --> 00:18:23.970
[THUNDERBOLT MOVE]

00:18:26.238 --> 00:18:28.874
[PAINED]

00:18:32.678 --> 00:18:35.147
Vivillon, no!
[STUNNED]

00:18:35.147 --> 00:18:36.916
WOMAN #1
'Vivillon is unable to battle!'

00:18:36.916 --> 00:18:38.951
Pikachu wins,
which means the winner

00:18:38.951 --> 00:18:40.453
of the match is Ash!

00:18:40.453 --> 00:18:41.854
Alright!

00:18:41.854 --> 00:18:43.522
[EXCITED]

00:18:43.522 --> 00:18:45.958
[laughs]
We did it, Pikachu!

00:18:45.958 --> 00:18:49.562
‐ Ash!
‐ Ash, that was amazing!

00:18:49.562 --> 00:18:52.832
Happy, happy, Bonnie!
Way to go, Ash.

00:18:52.832 --> 00:18:54.934
‐ You were great!
‐ Hey, thanks.

00:18:54.934 --> 00:18:57.436
And I couldn't have done it
without help from you guys.

00:18:57.436 --> 00:19:00.272
Ash, I had nothing to do
with your win and you know it.

00:19:00.272 --> 00:19:02.274
Nah, your invention
gave me the idea.

00:19:02.274 --> 00:19:03.542
Huh?

00:19:07.079 --> 00:19:09.715
You mean, my invention's
failure gave you the idea

00:19:09.715 --> 00:19:12.451
of Pikachu using
Electro Ball on itself?

00:19:12.451 --> 00:19:14.954
Yup, and that's why this victory
doesn't just belong to me.

00:19:14.954 --> 00:19:16.255
It's all of ours!

00:19:16.255 --> 00:19:18.958
[EMPHATIC]

00:19:18.958 --> 00:19:20.960
Thank you, Vivillon,
for a great battle.

00:19:20.960 --> 00:19:23.562
What did I tell you about Ash?

00:19:23.562 --> 00:19:26.899
[chuckles]
Yeah, you knew it all along.

00:19:26.899 --> 00:19:30.169
‐ Ash?
‐ Hey, Viola.

00:19:30.169 --> 00:19:32.171
Congratulations,
this is to prove you won

00:19:32.171 --> 00:19:34.173
your Gym battle against me.

00:19:34.173 --> 00:19:36.409
‐ 'The Bug Badge.'
‐ 'Thanks so much!'

00:19:38.310 --> 00:19:40.946
Alright!
I just got the Bug Badge!

00:19:40.946 --> 00:19:42.381
[PROUD]

00:19:48.654 --> 00:19:50.690
VIOLA 'There are some
things you can only see'

00:19:50.690 --> 00:19:53.125
when looking through
a camera's viewfinder.

00:19:53.125 --> 00:19:55.661
And things you'll only see
clearly by living together

00:19:55.661 --> 00:19:57.930
with Pokémon, keep strengthening
the bonds you share

00:19:57.930 --> 00:19:59.765
with your Pokémon
and good luck!

00:19:59.765 --> 00:20:02.468
Thanks.
[THANKFUL]

00:20:02.468 --> 00:20:05.971
Ash, I imagine you're heading
to your next Pokémon Gym battle.

00:20:05.971 --> 00:20:08.374
In that case, how about
the Gym in Cyllage City?

00:20:08.374 --> 00:20:11.844
Cyllage City Gym?
That sounds great.

00:20:11.844 --> 00:20:14.413
[EXCITED]/[SURPRISED]
You take care, Helioptile.

00:20:14.413 --> 00:20:16.115
[WARM]

00:20:17.717 --> 00:20:19.185
CLEMONT
Okay then, we're gonna head out!

00:20:19.185 --> 00:20:20.186
Thanks again.

00:20:20.186 --> 00:20:22.154
[THANKFUL]

00:20:22.154 --> 00:20:25.791
‐ Bye, bye!
‐ Viola, Alexa, Helioptile, bye!

00:20:25.791 --> 00:20:27.293
[WARM]

00:20:29.462 --> 00:20:33.766
I'll be seeing
you all again really soon.

00:20:33.766 --> 00:20:36.702
NARRATOR And so, after two
hard‐fought battles against

00:20:36.702 --> 00:20:40.272
Gym Leader Viola, Ash has
received the Bug Badge.

00:20:40.272 --> 00:20:42.508
Now, our heroes set off
to the Cyllage City Gym

00:20:42.508 --> 00:20:44.310
as the journey continues.

00:20:46.579 --> 00:20:48.848
So Serena, where are you
headed off to from here?

00:20:48.848 --> 00:20:50.616
Uh, me?

00:20:56.522 --> 00:20:58.124
[theme music]

